{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "萧秋水坠入漓江未死，被长江四棍（常无奇、宇文栋、金北望、孟东林）擒获。四人欲将其送往朱大天王处，为被杀的长江三英报仇。舟至高要停泊，常无奇等三人上岸采购，金北望欲挑断萧秋水脚筋。此时权力帮的钟无离、柳有孔伪装成镖师出现，杀死金北望，擒获萧秋水欲送往剑王屈寒山处。在街市上，一位黑布鞋白布袜青布衫的神秘文士出面阻拦，温言要求释放萧秋水，钟无离怒不可遏向其挥拳。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我不能杀他。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“便是这厮！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "text": "“慢！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文栋",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "text": "“怎地？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这人乃萧西楼之子，留着大有用处！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文栋",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "text": "“看来要个十万两不成问题。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“却闻浣花剑派已给权力帮铲了，自顾不及，哪有钱给？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“别管，先把他捞上来再说，死了的人，就没用了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文栋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“咱们一路上跟着，他人多势众，不好动手，却未料他自己摔落下来，正好替他们三个冤魂超度！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你们……是谁？咱们……无冤无仇……”",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你不知道我们是谁，我们却知道你是谁。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文栋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我们就是长江三峡，十二连环坞，水道天王大老爷，朱大天王的手下，‘三英四棍，五剑六掌，双神君’中的四条棍子。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我们一人一条棍子，打死你，替‘三英’报仇！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“他叫常无奇，”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“他叫宇文栋，”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“他叫金北望，”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我叫孟东林，”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你都认识了，那你躺下吧！”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们此处上岸，先采购点物品、再从水道到佛山，转到河源，赶陆路赴韩江，行动要快，天王要等急了，我们……”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文栋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“听说那鹰王也在广东，咱们行动，可要……”",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“咱们的形迹，要是让对方发现了，可死无葬身之地呀！”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“大不了可是往江中一跳，在陆上，咱们斗不过他，在水里，朱大天王的人还怕他们不成！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文栋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“咱们去采办，这小子留在这里，总是不妥，不如还是把他……”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“杀倒无妨，随便往江里一丢，便是了事。但天王要我们找到杀三英的凶手，现在只抓了一个，是不够的，不如把他擒到天王那里，再引出其他三人，才一并做了，也是大功一件。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这事就这样定了。现在还是有人上去采办要紧。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“我们三人上岸去，你留在这儿看船，看好这小子。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "text": "“这个当然。不过老大你们要早些回来，高要可是那‘剑王’的地头哩。”",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“办完事自会赶返，你在江湖上也扬了名立了万的，别怕成那个窝囊相。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“养你在船上，倒是吃住免费，不如……”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“先挑断你两条腿筋，也绝了你逃走的路！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“有人在里边吗？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“这是私船，在下是看守人，做主不得，还劳两位到别处去找。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“敢问这位仁兄，这舟渡不渡人？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“那多有打扰了，不好意思。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“我们过那边找，骚扰了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“哪里，哪里。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“对了，本来是要切断你的腿筋的，差些儿给忘了，他们反正上了岸，我就要断你双腿来乐乐。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“怎么这般烦人？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“对不起这位大爷，还有事要请教。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“去去去，这里是私船，不载客的！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“不载不载，我们知道，只要大爷指点一条明路，哪里有船可以搭乘？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“你不会去问本地人吗？！我才没空管你底事。”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“大爷你不是本地人吗？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“本地人这个口音吗？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“那就对了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "speaker_name": "金北望",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“什么对了？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_jin_bei_wang",
      "text": "“不是你对了，而是我们找对了。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“不错，就是他。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "text": "“老二好眼力，差些儿给这小子溜了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“咱们先把他的帮手做了，单他一人，逃不了的。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "text": "“不对，他似给人封了穴道。”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“原来是给在这儿的人所擒！看来咱们杀错人了！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "text": "“杀错了怎样？！那小子在咱们地盘上也抓人，咱权力帮就有权杀！你看他还藏有尖刀，我们不杀他，他就要杀我们！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“这小子怎样？要不要先刺瞎他的眼睛，我看他还瞪眼睛不！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "text": "“不行，反正他穴道被封，剑王还以为他死了，咱们送过去，必然奇功一件哩，又可顺此引那两个小子出来，咱们才可望报了大仇！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“咱们就这样提他到六星岩见剑王吗？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "text": "“怕什么？！这是咱们的地头！”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我这朋友，别的不好，就好喝点酒，现在烂醉如泥，随地乱吐，万一污了大家的地方，请恕罪则个！”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“这人没有醉，他只是给点了穴道。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“两位匆匆赶路，何不把此人穴道解开，不是可以走得更快？”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_wen_shi",
      "text": "“关你屁事！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“的确不关我事。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_wen_shi",
      "text": "“那你还不滚开？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“好，我让开。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“不过，你也要把人放开。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_wen_shi",
      "text": "“为什么？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“他也是人，他一定不喜欢被人拎着走路，何况他有两条腿，而且还是年轻人。”",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“想必阁下也不喜欢被人提着来走路吧！”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_wen_shi",
      "text": "“要不是我看你是个读书人，”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_wen_shi",
      "text": "“我早要你横尸当道了！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“阁下纵不把这青年放下来，至少也让他有说话的机会。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_wen_shi",
      "text": "“就凭你？！”",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_liu_you_kong",
